                "invention-title": [
                    "Central combustion type methane reforming hydrogen production reactor",
                    "一种中心燃烧式沼气重整制氢反应器"
                ]
            },
            "abstract": [
                {
                    "p": "The invention provides a central combustion type methane reforming hydrogen production reactor. The reforming hydrogen production reactor comprises a reactor shell, a reaction tube and a combustor; the furnace top of the reactor shell is connected with a reactor cover plate; the center of the reactor cover plate is connected with a combustor; a reactor cavity is formed in the reactor shell, and one part of each reaction tube penetrates through the reactor shell from the top of the reactor shell and is inserted into the reactor cavity. According to the technical scheme, the combustor is arranged in the center of the reforming hydrogen production reactor, flame generated by combustion of fuel gas directly heats the walls of all reaction tubes, the heat transfer speed is high, and the efficiency is high; after heat exchange, the flue gas is reflected by the bottom furnace wall of the reactor, reflows and rises to a flue gas outlet in the rear wall above the reactor and then is discharged, so that the flue gas energy utilization rate is further improved; the central combustion type methane reforming hydrogen production reactor is compact in structure, convenient to disassemble and assemble, uniform in heating inside the reaction tube, high in heat exchange efficiency and capable of effectively realizing a reforming hydrogen production reaction process."
                },
                {
                    "p": "本发明提供一种中心燃烧式沼气重整制氢反应器。重整制氢反应器包括反应器壳体、反应管和燃烧器；反应器壳体的炉顶连接有反应器盖板，反应器盖板中心连接有燃烧器；反应器壳体的内部具有反应器腔室，若干反应管的一部分从反应器壳体的顶部穿过反应器壳体，并插置于反应器腔室内。在本发明的技术方案中，重整制氢反应器中心位置布置燃烧器，燃气燃烧产生的火焰直接加热各反应管壁，传热速度快、效率高；换热后烟气经反应器底部炉墙反射回流上升至反应器上方后壁的烟气出口后排出，进一步提高烟气能量利用率；该中心燃烧式沼气重整制氢反应器结构紧凑、拆装方便，反应管内部受热均匀、换热效率高，能够有效实现重整制氢反应过程。"
                }
            ]
